  <brief_title>Gluten Immunity and Islet Autoimmunity in Type-1 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized Double-Masked Gluten Challenge to Evaluate Markers of Autoimmunity in Patients With Type-1 Diabetes and Celiac Disease After Oral Gluten Challenge</official_title>
